{"tid":772553,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"男子小便不順暢　竟自插耳機線進尿道導尿","createTime":"2018-08-09T00:37:36.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-22T10:32:07.000Z","uid":122,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"3037abd115fe4b33c2a817c7511a6ecd1e0f82c5","tid":772553,"uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-09T00:37:36.000Z","msg":"男子排尿不順暢，竟然自己將耳機線塞進尿道想導尿，結果卡住取不出，只好到醫院求助。<br />\n<br />\n據《看看新聞》報導，中國浙江橫店1名54歲男子，患有前列腺肥大症狀導致排尿困難，近來老毛病發作，為了省錢不去醫院，於是自己找了一條耳機線，塞進尿道想導尿，沒想到卡住男以取出，到醫院就醫後手術取出。醫師提醒導尿絕對不能自己動手，一定要到醫院處理。（即時新聞中心／綜合報導）"},{"pid":"01c8e0729ced368e9b2047528cf23869e978f77a","tid":772553,"uid":85557,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-09T00:41:52.000Z","msg":"睇字都覺得痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nBtw男你老母"},{"pid":"c3c909814b4c30f8702c4bbb255f90e0427dc42e","tid":772553,"uid":190066,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-09T00:45:06.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d24953c3a2069e6e6f42d98edb3efc6918713ec4","tid":772553,"uid":49245,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-09T00:46:53.000Z","msg":"又贏"},{"pid":"ae1055caf1fe0ff70dd30287b97f672d42aaf6a6","tid":772553,"uid":5102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-09T00:47:37.000Z","msg":"笑死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f2d33d61ef0c079a37648cee3476fe98ca6722a","tid":772553,"uid":76301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-09T00:51:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n應該好痛"},{"pid":"5e9c67572973c8ad6278009d4d7c1ad413aa2c68","tid":772553,"uid":129521,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-09T01:16:18.000Z","msg":"一時